[32m+[m[32m## Build Android APK[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThis project is configured to generate an installable Android **APK** with the EAS `preview` profile.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32mnpm run build:apk[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mFor Play Store upload builds (`.aab`):[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
