[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Parent app features[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- Parent login using SchoolSync account credentials[m
[32m+[m[32m- View linked children[m
[32m+[m[32m- View attendance (last 30 days)[m
[32m+[m[32m- View marks/exam results[m
[32m+[m[32m- View class timetable[m
[32m+[m[32m- View school announcements[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe app reads backend base URL from:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32mEXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=...[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mCurrent local setup points to production in `.env.local`.[m
